Class DataContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • omni.database.DataContainer

  • public class DataContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    This class provides data container for omni data extracted from catfish and mongodb, and thus is memory intensive.

      • initialize

        public static void initialize(java.util.List<java.lang.String> appIds,
                              java.lang.String instinctCall)
        This method sets necessary data container for precheck phase.

        Because some attributes from applications may not be available at this phase, only parts of the container are required.

        Parameters:
        appIds - application ids to process.
        instinctCall - supports "precheck" only.
